snippet.title: Windblown Official Announcement Trailer | The Game Awards 2023
snippet.description:
Welcome to Windblown! Dead Cells’ hyperactive, sugar-rushed 3D sibling.  

You play as a Leaper; one of our heroes, on a mission to defend the Ark from a very aggro Vortex. Absorb memories of fallen warriors, and then put them to good use by infusing their skills into your weapons. It’s what they would have wanted...  

Dodge death solo, or with up to 2 friends!  

Get ready to dash, die, and repeat!! Early Access launches in 2024, join our communities and help us shape this game!  

#tga2023 #motiontwin #gaming
